## Refactor — collapse duplicated change-audit diff loops

### Context

Refactor pass (Fowler, behaviour-preserving) on the audit-trail code added
above. The two bulk-diff recorders each carried six near-identical
`record_change` loops differing only by entity type and verb.

### Changes

1. `src/back/objects/ontology/Ontology.py`
